PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of PAUL-H. BILODEAU, of Sillery, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Shavak Madon, who has resigned.
